Class ConfConstants

java.lang.Object
  com.github.dandelion.datatables.core.constants.ConfConstants

public class ConfConstants
extends Object

Dandelion-datatables configuration related constants.

Note to developers: all constants that exist in the datatables-default.properties file must appear in this class in order to be checked by the isValidProperty method of.

Author:
Thibault Duchateau
